OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fvery warm evening for many and staying
OL,7,Fsunny for most. Scattered
OL,8,Fthunderstorms are possible,
OL,9,Fpotentially bringing large hail and
OL,10,Ffrequent lightning but most places
OL,11,Fwill stay entirely dry. Remaining
OL,12,Frather warm overnight with often clear
OL,13,Fskies.
OL,14,
OL,15,CWednesday:FAnother largely dry and
OL,16,Ffine day with plenty of sunshine.
OL,17,FFeeling quite a bit less hot than on
OL,18,FTuesday, with an easterly breeze, but
OL,19,Fstill very warm. Isolated showers
OL,20,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
