OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying largely dry with some sunshine
OL,7,Fbut the odd shower is possible at
OL,8,Ftimes. Very warm initially but it will
OL,9,Fbegin to cool a little by the weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
